001
002package com.commercetools.http.okhttp4;
003
004import java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService;
005import java.util.function.Supplier;
006
007import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.BaseHttpClientSupplier;
008import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.VrapHttpClient;
009
010public class OkHttp4ClientSupplier extends BaseHttpClientSupplier {
011
012    @Override
013    public VrapHttpClient get() {
014        return new CtOkHttp4Client();
015    }
016
017    @Override
018    public Supplier<VrapHttpClient> get(ExecutorService executorService) {
019        return () -> new CtOkHttp4Client(executorService);
020    }
021}
